text: José Manuel Díaz Gallego (born 18 January 1995 in Jaén) is a Spanish cyclist, who currently rides for UCI ProTeam . ==Major results== ;2017 : 10th Gran Premio di Lugano : 10th Pro Ötztaler 5500 ;2019 : 1st 20px Mountains classification Czech Cycling Tour ;2020 : 10th Overall Tour of Rwanda ::1st Stage 8 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male cyclists
